{"title":"长青藤——献给红军长征胜利六十周年","authors":["曾凡华"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长青藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给红军长征胜利六十周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾凡华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一条长长青青的藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过记忆的断崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬上峰顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五岭从远方逶迤而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如戏珠之龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气吞云梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种诗的意境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便油然而生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"６０年前那场艰难的行军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今已进入沙盘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入地图"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为创世纪的风流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而那些落难者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却在旷古的沉寂里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默滋养着革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如藤上的须根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸存的幸存者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"则成为叶子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为葱郁的形象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向世界昭告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九死一生的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不会凋零"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风也罢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬雪也罢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是过眼云烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倔强的主干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是青青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是在风刀霜剑的欺压中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前延伸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自然是曲曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自然也弯弯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲曲弯弯的挫折里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产生伟大的螺旋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路是藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意志是藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军是藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义是藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长长青青的藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有不死的精魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在干渴而少养分的日子里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着磐石的纹脉和甘泉的缝隙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦苦地寻觅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最终在那片黄土塬上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得以生存"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得以壮大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得以凤凰涅槃般的飞升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从那场远征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入斯诺的笔记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入剑桥史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西方便为之瞩目"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为之颤栗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支藤一样的队伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以藤一样的韧力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拱破了旧世界的平衡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也将以藤的执著"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藤的勇毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续其新的征程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管匍匐的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨如晦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难丛生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但英雄的格局已定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都无法阻止它的攀援和前进"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}